<DefaultLayout>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mx-4 md:mx-16 my-10">
        <h1>CPES Paris-Saclay</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">Data Science, Society and Health</p>

        <h2>An excellence program at the heart of the Saclay plateau</h2>

        <p>The Multidisciplinary Cycle of Higher Education (CPES) is a high-level 3-year program, delivering a diploma equivalent to a <strong>Bachelor's degree</strong>.</p>

        <p>Launched in September 2023 at the Lycée International de Palaiseau Paris-Saclay (LIPPS), this curriculum is the result of an unprecedented collaboration between five prestigious institutions:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Lycée International de Palaiseau Paris-Saclay (LIPPS)</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Université Paris-Saclay</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Institut Polytechnique de Paris</strong></li>
            <li><strong>HEC Paris</strong></li>
            <li><strong>ENS Paris-Saclay</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why choose this CPES?</h2>

        <p>It's a future-oriented program, designed to meet the growing needs for data science expertise across all sectors. It offers:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>A hybrid pedagogy</strong>: The best of preparatory classes (personalized support) and university/grandes écoles (research, projects).</li>
            <li><strong>Research-based training</strong>: From the 1st year, with lab visits, conferences and concrete projects.</li>
            <li><strong>Multidisciplinary openness</strong>: Mathematics, Computer Science, but also Economics, Sociology or Biology depending on your track.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 my-8">
            <a href="a-propos" class="btn btn-primary max-sm:w-full">Learn more about the program</a>
            <a href="contact" class="btn btn-secondary max-sm:w-full">Contact us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <Hero1 />
    <Partenaires />
</DefaultLayout>
